targets.rawSql:
select distinct
now() as time
, concat(h.host, '|',e.severity, '|',e.name) as "FALHA"
from hstgrp g, hosts_groups hg, hosts h, items i, functions f, triggers t, events e
where g.groupid = hg.groupid
and (hg.hostid,h.hostid,i.hostid,i.itemid,f.triggerid,e.objectid) = (h.hostid,i.hostid,hg.hostid,f.itemid,e.objectid,t.triggerid)
--and a.eventid = e.eventid
--and a.message !~ 'PROBLEM|RESOLVED'
and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
and g.name ~ '^INF/.*/DF'
and e.severity in (4,5)
--and to_timestamp(e.clock) > (now() - Interval '30 day')
and $__unixEpochFilter(e.clock)
and t.value::text ~ '1'
and t.status = 0
and e.value = 1
and h.host ~* '${hosts:pipe}';

select now() as time, CONCAT(name,'|',severidade,'|',evento,'|',mensagem,'|',clock) as "FALHA"
from (
     select t.name,t.severidade,t.evento,a.message as mensagem,t.clock
     from (  
          select t.eventid,t.name, e.severity as severidade, t.evento, to_timestamp(e.clock) as clock
          from (
               select distinct t.eventid,t.name,t.evento
               from (
                    select distinct e.eventid, t.name, e.name as evento
                    from (
                         select distinct
                                t.triggerid
                              , h.hostid
                              , h.name
                           from hosts h, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g, items i, functions f, triggers t
                          where t.triggerid = f.triggerid
                            and f.itemid = i.itemid
                            and i.hostid = h.hostid
                            and h.hostid = hg.hostid
                            and hg.groupid = g.groupid
                            and g.name ~ '^INF/.*/DF'
                            and h.host ~* '${hosts:pipe}'
                            and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
                            and t.status = 0
                            and t.value = 1
                            and t.priority in (4,5)
                    ) t, events e
                    where t.triggerid = e.objectid
                      and e.severity in (4,5)
                      and e.value = 1
                      and e.source = 0
                      and e.name ~ 'Indisponível|Tempo de Propagação|Erros'
                      and to_timestamp(e.clock) between (now() - interval '30 day') and now()
               ) t left join event_recovery r on r.eventid = t.eventid
               where r.r_eventid is null
          ) t, events e
          where e.eventid = t.eventid
     ) t left join acknowledges a on a.eventid = t.eventid
     order by t.name, t.clock desc
) t

targets.rawSql:
select distinct
h.host as "Dispositivo", e.name as "Evento"
from hstgrp g, hosts_groups hg, hosts h, items i, functions f, triggers t, events e
where g.groupid = hg.groupid
and (hg.hostid,h.hostid,i.hostid,i.itemid,f.triggerid,e.objectid) = (h.hostid,i.hostid,hg.hostid,f.itemid,e.objectid,t.triggerid)
--and a.eventid = e.eventid
--and a.message !~ 'PROBLEM|RESOLVED'
and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
and g.name ~ '^INF/.*/DF'
and e.severity in (4,5)
--and to_timestamp(e.clock) > (now() - Interval '30 day')
and $__unixEpochFilter(e.clock)
and t.value::text ~ '1'
and t.status = 0
and e.value = 1
and h.host ~* '${hosts:pipe}'
and e.name ~* 'ERROS|INDISPONÍVEL|TEMPO DE PROPAGAÇÃO'

select distinct name as "Dispositivo",evento as "Evento"
from (
     select t.name,t.severidade,t.evento,a.message as mensagem,t.clock
     from (  
          select t.eventid,t.name, e.severity as severidade, t.evento, to_timestamp(e.clock) as clock
          from (
               select distinct t.eventid,t.name,t.evento
               from (
                    select distinct e.eventid, t.name, e.name as evento
                    from (
                         select distinct
                                t.triggerid
                              , h.hostid
                              , h.name
                           from hosts h, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g, items i, functions f, triggers t
                          where t.triggerid = f.triggerid
                            and f.itemid = i.itemid
                            and i.hostid = h.hostid
                            and h.hostid = hg.hostid
                            and hg.groupid = g.groupid
                            and g.name ~ '^INF/.*/DF'
                            and h.host ~* '${hosts:pipe}'
                            and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
                            and t.status = 0
                            and t.value = 1
                            and t.priority in (4,5)
                    ) t, events e
                    where t.triggerid = e.objectid
                      and e.severity in (4,5)
                      and e.value = 1
                      and e.source = 0
                      and e.name ~ 'Indisponível|Tempo de Propagação|Erros'
                      and to_timestamp(e.clock) between (now() - interval '30 day') and now()
               ) t left join event_recovery r on r.eventid = t.eventid
               where r.r_eventid is null
          ) t, events e
          where e.eventid = t.eventid
     ) t left join acknowledges a on a.eventid = t.eventid
     order by t.name, t.clock desc
) t

select distinct concat(h.name,'___',split_part(i.name,' :: ',2),'___', split_part(split_part(i.name,' :: ',3),'_',1)  )
   from host_inventory hi, hosts h, interface int, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g, items i
 where 
   (hi.hostid,h.hostid,int.hostid,hg.hostid,i.hostid,hg.groupid) = (h.hostid,int.hostid,hg.hostid,hi.hostid,h.hostid,g.groupid)
   and g.name ~ 'INF/.*/(DF).*'
   and (i.status,h.status) = (0,0)
   and i.name ~ '(VLAN|INTERNET|VIDEOCONF|UPLINK|TELEFONIA)_modelo'  
   and i.name ~ '^Tr.fego_HC_Entrada'
